21.2.
In case of any difficulty, question or concern about this Privacy Policy, please contact the Operator’s Data Protection Officer on the DPO Email, dpo@leovegas.com.
21.3.
Your acceptance of these T&Cs includes Your full acceptance of the Operator’s Privacy Policy which is included by reference in these T&Cs.
22. Complaints and Dispute Resolution
22.1.
If You have a complaint, You can contact the Operator on the Customer Support Contact as indicated in these T&Cs. The Operator’s team members will endeavour to reply to You within 10 days, unless there are external factors causing delays.
22.2.
The Operator will use its reasonable efforts to resolve a reported matter promptly.
